    "en": {
      "name": "Nekroz Divinemirror",
      "effect": "During the Main Phase: Ritual Summon 1 \"Nekroz\" Ritual Monster from your hand or banishment, by Tributing monsters from your hand and/or field, and/or sending \"Nekroz\" monsters from your Extra Deck to the GY, whose total Levels equal or exceed its Level. During your Main Phase: You can banish this card and 1 \"Nekroz\" monster from your GY; add 1 \"Nekroz\" Spell from your Deck to your hand. You can only use each effect of \"Nekroz Divinemirror\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
